title: Will.I.Am Interview and More
itunes:title: Will.I.Am Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had Will.I.Am stop by, and speak to us about Mercedes Benz Collab, The Future Of Tech, NFTs, Eazy-E Mentorship and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to another Floridian for throwing a bucket of pee towards her neighbor because of his chickens going to her lawn. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" especially the last caller, that sounded like Tyler Perry himself produced her story!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
